this morning. âª

22:07.480 --> 22:09.319
Catflap, please.

22:10.319 --> 22:13.319
MUMBLES ANGRILY

22:17.440 --> 22:18.840
I'm next.

22:21.319 --> 22:22.720
You all right?

22:22.720 --> 22:25.279
I was, aye, but now
I feel a wee bit jumpy.

22:27.680 --> 22:30.799
Listen, all we want out of this is
for one of the two of us to win it.

22:30.799 --> 22:32.799
You've got every chance
in the world.

22:34.960 --> 22:37.120
Thanks, Jack. So do you.

22:37.119 --> 22:41.079
Just go in there
and be the best version of yourself.

22:44.200 --> 22:47.640
IMITATES SEAN CONNERY
I love the beaches, the shand,

22:47.640 --> 22:49.120
the shurf...

22:50.640 --> 22:52.720
...the sheashells.

22:52.720 --> 22:55.759
I also like barbecuesh.

22:55.759 --> 23:01.879
I like...chopsh, ribsh, and, erm...

23:02.960 --> 23:05.200
...and shaushagesh.

23:05.200 --> 23:09.400
AMERICAN ACCENT: Has anyone told you
you sound a bit like Sean Connery?

23:10.759 --> 23:12.480
It hash been shaid.

23:13.480 --> 23:14.960
Thanks for coming in.

23:16.759 --> 23:18.000
Shanksh.

23:21.279 --> 23:25.038
First three weeks, no wages,
until I'm paid back.

23:25.038 --> 23:26.959
After that, you make good money.

23:26.960 --> 23:29.120
Thanks, Mr Harrid.

23:29.119 --> 23:31.879
I really do appreciate the
opportunity. I won't let you down.

23:31.880 --> 23:33.040
Good lad.

23:35.599 --> 23:37.359
Hi.

23:40.519 --> 23:42.158
So, it's Eesa?

23:42.160 --> 23:47.480
No, Isa, like Liza. Minnelli.
Drennan.

23:47.480 --> 23:51.480
I see you didn't put your age.
No.

23:51.480 --> 23:54.920
A lady never discusses her age.

23:54.920 --> 23:56.840
ELASTIC PINGS

24:01.359 --> 24:04.439
You see, Mr Mullen,
the couple we are looking for

24:04.440 --> 24:10.000
have to have that outdoor glow,
that sea-sprayed sparkle,

24:10.000 --> 24:14.400
a face that says, "I've had a life
and I'm still living it."

24:15.519 --> 24:17.720
Have you had any work done?

24:20.119 --> 24:23.599
I am aghast, shocked and horrified

24:23.599 --> 24:26.439
that you would even suggest
such a thing.

24:29.079 --> 24:31.839
Thanks very much, Mr Jarvis.

24:31.839 --> 24:33.559
It was a pleasure meeting you.

24:33.559 --> 24:35.960
Oh, is that it? Oh, well,
if you'd allow me for a second...

24:35.960 --> 24:37.840
The ladies love this, by the way.

24:47.400 --> 24:51.519
