OK, that's enough of that.
Thank you.

25:09.720 --> 25:12.759
Oh...oh, oh!

25:17.720 --> 25:20.519
Ha! No way, man!
The Wolf's got a job!

25:20.519 --> 25:23.839
All these papers are heavy
and my legs are killing me.

25:23.839 --> 25:25.319
See you later, mate.

25:29.599 --> 25:32.119
Good job, Winston.

25:32.119 --> 25:34.919
Aye, you're welcome, Joe.
A bet's a bet.

25:53.400 --> 25:55.640
Can I no put a catflap
in my door an' all

25:55.640 --> 25:57.800
and we can share the bloody cat?

25:57.799 --> 26:00.279
I'm no the sharing type, Winston.

26:00.279 --> 26:04.559
I won the bet, and what's mine's
mine. That's the way I like it.

26:04.559 --> 26:05.798
MEOW

26:05.799 --> 26:07.919
I thought you suited that beard.

26:07.920 --> 26:12.680
Aye, but once I knew I'd lost,
I just wanted it off, you know?

26:12.680 --> 26:14.720
I see you're back to 5'2".

26:14.720 --> 26:17.680
5'8", you cheeky big bastard.

26:19.160 --> 26:22.680
Me dyeing my hair
Paul-McCartney-brown, as well.

26:22.680 --> 26:25.640
And it'll no be long
till you're back to normal.

26:26.799 --> 26:29.919
The bastard on the 42
widnae accept my bus pass.

26:29.920 --> 26:32.000
I had to pay full price!

26:32.000 --> 26:34.039
WHIMPERS

26:35.839 --> 26:40.519
Say hello to Mr...Twilight.

26:42.359 --> 26:45.119
Aw, Shug!

26:46.799 --> 26:49.159
Well done, Shug.
Well deserved, Shug.

26:49.160 --> 26:50.798
What can I tell you, eh?

26:50.799 --> 26:54.079
My years in the Navy.
My specialised skill-set.

26:54.079 --> 26:56.039
I am an outdoor man.

26:56.039 --> 26:58.480
What about the wig?
Oh, they never even noticed it.

26:58.480 --> 27:01.680
To Mr Twilight - Shug!

27:02.680 --> 27:04.320
And Mrs Twilight -

27:04.319 --> 27:05.480
Edith!

27:12.400 --> 27:14.240
Wow, Edith.

27:14.240 --> 27:17.440
You look hu...human.

27:19.480 --> 27:21.480
What did you do wi'
your hairy moles?

27:21.480 --> 27:25.400
They took them aff.
There's a wee keepsake.

27:29.559 --> 27:30.759
And your hump?

27:30.759 --> 27:33.519
Turns out it wisnae
curvature of the spine.

27:33.519 --> 27:35.920
It was just fluid.

27:37.200 --> 27:39.039
JACK GAGS

27:40.480 --> 27:45.880
What can I get the glamorous girl?
A pina colada? A Cuba libre?

27:45.880 --> 27:47.600
Pint of Guinness.

28:16.920 --> 28:20.759
Look who it is, Joe.
A wolf in sheepish clothing.

28:20.759 --> 28:22.960
I'm sorry, Joe.

28:22.960 --> 28:25.639
My feet were sore
and I just wanted a shot.

28:25.638 --> 28:29.438
Nae harm done, son.
We'll say no more about it.

28:29.440 --> 28:32.919
You're lucky, son. Another chance.

28:32.919 --> 28:34.759
You are at a fork in the road.

28:34.759 --> 28:38.240
Down one path,
a life of petty crime and infamy.

28:38.240 --> 28:43.759
The other road?
Hard work, reward, respect.

